Package org.openwms.core.configuration.impl.file

Class GenericPreference

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openwms.core.configuration.impl.file.AbstractPreference
      • org.openwms.core.configuration.impl.file.GenericPreference
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ApplicationPreference, ModulePreference, RolePreference, UserPreference
    public abstract class GenericPreference
extends AbstractPreference
implements Serializable
    An GenericPreference is a superclass for all other preference classes within the application. It encapsulates some common behavior of preference types.
    Author:
    Heiko Scherrer
